title: Nemanja Stojić
text: Nemanja Stojić (; born 15 January 1998) is a <a href="Serbs">Serbian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29%23centre-back">centre-back</a> who plays for Serbian side <a href="FK%20Metalac%20Gornji%20Milanovac">Metalac</a>.
